window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Tess Morrigan, my fated mate, is my mortal enemy.</p> <p>She's been working for the monster I hate the most: Lucifer, my father.</p> <p>She won't stop until she has my head on a golden platter.</p> <p>Each time we meet, her eyes spark with passion and dreams, and her lips taste like honey.</p> <p>Keep your enemies close.</p> <p>So, I trap her in my embrace.</p> <p>Touching her. Desiring her.</p> <p>Until the day I strike first.</p> <p>Best-selling author of Half-Blood Academy, Meg Xuemei X takes you on a wild ride in this sinfully steamy enemies-to-lovers romance perfect for fans of Ilona Andrews, Amelia Hutchins, Laura Thalassa, C. N. Crawford, Karen Marie Moning, and Sarah J. Massa.</p>"; 
